<view class="container" style="padding-bottom: 150rpx;">
  <view class="tips">
    <text class="tips-title">发帖须知：</text>
    <text>1. 专注甲板船领域交流（造船/设计/设备/船级社/法规等）。</text>
    <text>2. 严禁发布违法违规内容。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="form-group">
    <textarea 
      class="input-area" 
      placeholder="请输入您的帖子内容..." 
      model:value="{{content}}"
      maxlength="500"
    ></textarea>
    <view class="char-count">{{content.length}}/500</view>
  </view>
  
  <button class="btn-submit" type="primary" bindtap="submit" disabled="{{submitting}}">发布帖子</button>

</view>
